description:
The course is aimed to help you practice for TOEFL IBT. Preparation for TOEFL test is very important and I can provide you with my experience in getting 107/120 points for TOEFL.

TOEFL Preparation course is separated in 5 sections, 4 of which are as in actual TOEFL test. Each section shows you the question types and small hints to improve your answering. Also, each section provides my 5 to 6 tips generally to score higher.

I show you the materials I have used for listening, reading, writing and speaking as well. If you need some practical advice, please sign up! I look forward to seeing you inside the course.

!!!If you liked this course after completion, please, leave a review. It will help us make the course better for other students and add some extra value for you. Thank you!!!
title: Get the high result with TOEFL IBT Preparation Guide!
